Meet or exceed sales targets for multiple relevant outsourcing services offered by Dikshatek;
Ensure increased growth profitability (Quarterly KPIs and targets) set by BD Manager;
Strengthen a streamlined pipeline of future key accounts to take & bring new profitable business leads to the Talent Acquisition Team (TAT);

