Proactively lead account meetings and communications to ensure all relevant stakeholders at Dikshatek are educated on the account requirements; and are engaged with these clients;
Partner closely with TAT, Sales Team to ensure the smooth operations of serving practices & account allocations for fulfilment;
Deliver the best quality of service standards to clients by playing a role of connector between Dikshatek & client stakeholders;
Timely generate reports of customer and prospect status and management to BD Manager.

Job requirements
At least 2 years proven track record in sales & business development;
Big plus with knowledge of models including HR outsourcing, IT consulting service industry, including trends, key players, and competitors;
